EDI Document 997 - Functional Acknowledgment
Function:
The EDI 997 Functional Acknowledgment document is used to confirm the receipt of an EDI transaction. It indicates whether the transaction was successfully received and processed.

Example:

ISA*00*          *00*          *ZZ*SENDERID      *ZZ*RECEIVERID    *YYMMDD*HHMM*U*00501*000000001*0*P*>~
GS*FA*SENDERID*RECEIVERID*YYMMDD*HHMM*1*X*005010~
ST*997*0001~
AK1*PO*ORIGINAL TRANSACTION SET PURPOSE CODE~
AK2*810*ORIGINAL TRANSACTION SET CONTROL NUMBER*20230701~
AK5*A~
AK9*A*1*1*1~
SE*8*0001~
GE*1*1~
IEA*1*000000001~

Purpose in Lizgate Enterprise:
In Lizgate Enterprise, the EDI 997 document enhances transaction reliability by providing confirmation of receipt and processing of EDI transactions, ensuring data integrity and facilitating timely issue resolution.